

    Prerequisites

* libcurl   7.18.0+  <http://curl.haxx.se/>
* libpcre   7.8.0+   <http://pcre.org/>
* libiconv  1.12.0+  <http://www.gnu.org/software/libiconv/>


    Installation

./configure && make install

See also ./configure --help. For example, --disable-exe disables compilation
and installation of the quvi(1) executable.

"make dox" generates the C API documentation using doxygen.
The current documentation is also available at:
    http://quvi.googlecode.com/svn/docs/html/index.html


